About Us
hero video paused, press to play video
Playing hero video, press to pause video
Welcome to Deck 84, the ultimate outdoor dining restaurant in Delray Beach. Renowned as one of the top al fresco restaurants in the area, Deck 84 has been a go-to restaurant on Atlantic Avenue in Delray Beach since 2010.
Catering to locals, boaters and tourists alike, Deck 84's expansive menu allows something for everyone! Discover why we're known not only for our exceptional American favorites but also as the go-to destination for the best poke bowls in Delray Beach. The menu boasts a variety of options, from mouthwatering prime beef burgers and refreshing salads to fresh seafood creations and sharable plates. Bring the whole family; Deck 84 offers a kid menu and doggie menu!
Explore the most recent media features and accolades of Deck 84, including consecutive years of winning the TripAdvisor Travelers' Choice award, recognitions for the Best Happy Hour, Best Bar for Live Music, and more!
For media inquiries or more information, send requests to: Amber@axispointco.com
